ress.com/2017/07/ixion-theme-options.jpg?w=840\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n	\n		\n		\n\n		\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"The Next Chapter for Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/07/28/the-next-chapter-for-themes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/07/28/the-next-chapter-for-themes/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 28 Jul 2017 15:45:45 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Gutenberg\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://themeshaper.com/?p=6836\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:698:\"Every few months I read a post about how the WordPress theme business has shrunk. The authors always reach a similar conclusion. Sales have dwindled. Competition has increased. Putting food on the table, finding a niche and standing out is near impossible. It may not be so impossible though. With a new editing interface on &#8230; <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/07/28/the-next-chapter-for-themes/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> \"The Next Chapter for&#160;Themes\"</span></a><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6836&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"David A. Kennedy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3677:\"<p>Every few months I read a post about how the WordPress theme business has shrunk. The authors always reach a similar conclusion. Sales have dwindled. Competition has increased. Putting food on the table, finding a niche and standing out is near impossible.</p>\n<p>It may not be so impossible though. With a <a href=\"https://wordpress.github.io/gutenberg/\">new editing interface on the horizon</a>, the theme landscape will change in a big way. That editing interface, and eventually better site customization, means we (those who create themes) will all have a chance to redefine what a theme is and means to people who use WordPress. It will be new, fertile ground to discover – the next chapter for themes. We just can&#8217;t make the same mistakes we&#8217;ve made before.</p>\n<p>A long time ago, especially in Internet years, you could sell a collection of well-designed WordPress themes and make a living. These became known in the WordPress space as premium themes. What made them &#8220;premium&#8221; was loosely defined. They often sported a unique look or carried interesting features. As a consumer, premium themes always seemed more special to me. They took risks. That runs against what we say on the Theme Team at WordPress.com, where we do nothing but create WordPress themes: The only difference between a free theme and a premium one is the price.</p>\n<p>As more and more theme shops sprang up, the feature race began. Many themes became as complex as WordPress itself. Designers and developers had less time to experiment because we spent more time glancing over our shoulders. What&#8217;s the next trend? What&#8217;s this other theme shop doing?</p>\n<p>To correct for the complexity, the larger theme ecosystem became obsessed with standards. Like making sure a theme did things the WordPress way or always met &#8220;best practices.&#8221; The web industry as a whole also continues to obsess over and rely on build tools and frameworks, sometimes to a fault. They should solve technical hurdles for us. But do they? Sometimes they do at the expense of our customers. Make no mistake, I&#8217;m not arguing against best practices or tools. We do the <a href=\"https://underscores.me/\">same</a> <a href=\"https://developer.wordpress.com/themes/\">thing</a>. However, the status quo, even if it means well, can blind you to what&#8217;s important.</p>\n<p>What&#8217;s important, you ask? Our customers. Doing the invisible things that make their experience its best. Focusing on accessibility, performance and security. Making sure the the small screens look just as good as the large screens. <a href=\"https://wordpress.github.io/gutenberg/\">Gutenberg</a>, the project name for the new editing interface, will make one theme become many. A customer using a theme will be able to bend it many different ways – <strong>turning the focal point of the theme from its capabilities to its design</strong>.</p>\n<p>Customers want their sites to look just right. They don&#8217;t want to learn a theme. So when the new age of themes begins, <em>promise me you&#8217;ll focus on what they want</em>. You won&#8217;t get distracted by the many different ways to extend this new editor or become mired in all the ways to prevent the abuse of customizing it.</p>\n<p>This matters. Your customers need you. And you&#8217;ll stand out and put more food on your table.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://pixabay.com/en/book-open-pages-library-books-408302/\"><em>Photo courtesy of Hermann</em></a>.</p><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6836&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/07/28/the-next-chapter-for-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"5\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:3:\"url\";s:73:\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/07/pexels-photo-2675861.jpeg\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"content\";a:2:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:72:\"http://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/07/pexels-photo-2675861.jpeg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"pexels-photo-267586\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:82:\"http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/219860d3117df777c48f475d25e24fdd?s=96&d=identicon&r=G\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"davidalankennedy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n	\n		\n		\n\n		\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"The Developer’s Guide to Supporting Your Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/07/25/the-developers-guide-to-supporting-your-themes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:91:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/07/25/the-developers-guide-to-supporting-your-themes/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 25 Jul 2017 18:03:08 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Community\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Education\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"theme support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://themeshaper.com/?p=6822\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:764:\"At this year&#8217;s WordCamp Europe, some members of the WordPress.org support team brainstormed how we might be able to share support skills and strategies with the broader WordPress community. We decided to offer some workshops to share support knowledge, and the first one –  by yours truly – has been announced. Details are below. Hope &#8230; <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/07/25/the-developers-guide-to-supporting-your-themes/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> \"The Developer&#8217;s Guide to Supporting Your&#160;Themes\"</span></a><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6822&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Kathryn P.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2845:\"<p>At this year&#8217;s WordCamp Europe, some members of the WordPress.org support team brainstormed how we might be able to share support skills and strategies with the broader WordPress community. We decided to offer some workshops to share support knowledge, and the first one –  by yours truly – <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/support/2017/07/the-developers-guide-to-supporting-your-themes-a-support-workshop/\">has been announced</a>. Details are below.</p>\n<p>Hope to see you there!</p>\n<p><strong>Update:</strong> <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/support/2017/08/supporting-themes/\">The recording, slides, and notes are available.</a></p>\n<h3>The Developer&#8217;s Guide to Supporting Your Themes</h3>\n<p>Providing support for your themes offers tremendous opportunities to educate WordPress users, from explaining how to make a child theme to offering simple CSS customizations. It also presents challenges, like figuring out how to help people who aren’t tech-savvy or need support beyond the scope of what you can provide. While many developers dread doing support, with some concrete strategies and techniques in hand, helping users doesn’t have to be a chore – and can even be fun! This session looks at how to make your themes’ users happy while feeling a sense of satisfaction from your own support efforts – a winning combination in the world of theme development.</p>\n<h3>When</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20170823T1600\">Wednesday, August 23, 2017, 16:00 UTC.</a> It will last for an hour and include Q&amp;A.</p>\n<h3>How</h3>\n<p>The session will be run via videoconference and will be recorded and posted later for those who can&#8217;t make it. Please <a href=\"https://zoom.us/download\">download</a> the free Zoom app ahead of time. You can run Zoom on most <a href=\"https://support.zoom.us/hc/en-us/articles/201362023-System-Requirements-for-PC-Mac-and-Linux\">desktop and mobile devices</a>.</p>\n<p>A link to the Zoom teleconference will be provided in the <span class=\"tag-prefix\">#</span>forums WordPress.org Slack channel about 10 minutes before the session begins.</p>\n<h3>Who</h3>\n<p>In her role as Theme Whisperer on the Theme Team at Automattic, <a href=\"https://kpresner.com/\">Kathryn Presner</a> provides support for hundreds of themes. She began helping people as a volunteer in the WordPress.org forums back in 2011 and was immediately hooked.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em>Featured image by <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/techthis/6822635210/\">Pixel Fantasy</a> (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/2.0/\">CC BY-NC-ND 2.0</a>)</em></p><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6822&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/07/25/the-developers-guide-to-supporting-your-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"5\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:3:\"url\";s:71:\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/07/support-rainbow-sm1.jpg\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"content\";a:2:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:70:\"http://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/07/support-rainbow-sm1.jpg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\"support\" on a colored background\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:82:\"http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/88ff758a54124a679af2e4cdaae8ba62?s=96&d=identicon&r=G\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"kathrynwp\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n	\n		\n		\n\n		\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"The Future of Underscores and A New Committer\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/06/26/the-future-of-underscores-and-a-new-committer/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/06/26/the-future-of-underscores-and-a-new-committer/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 26 Jun 2017 19:02:40 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Theme Development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Components\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"underscores\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"_s\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://themeshaper.com/?p=6793\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:767:\"The title may strike you as a bit ominous, but fear not. Underscores, our popular starter theme for WordPress theme development, isn&#8217;t going anywhere. As we continue to push for consistency in themes and imagine what they might become with Gutenberg, we’re bringing our attention back to Underscores. 🚀 For the last year and a half, we&#8217;ve &#8230; <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/06/26/the-future-of-underscores-and-a-new-committer/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> \"The Future of Underscores and A New&#160;Committer\"</span></a><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6793&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"David A. Kennedy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3295:\"<p>The title may strike you as a bit ominous, but fear not. <a href=\"http://underscores.me/\">Underscores</a>, our popular starter theme for WordPress theme development, isn&#8217;t going anywhere. As we continue to push for consistency in themes and imagine what they might become with <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg\">Gutenberg</a>, we’re bringing our attention back to Underscores. <img src=\"https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/mu-plugins/wpcom-smileys/twemoji/2/72x72/1f680.png\" alt=\"🚀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p>For the last year and a half, we&#8217;ve experimented with a new starter-theme generator called <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2016/02/09/introducing-components/\">Components</a>. It was a way to make a few different theme &#8220;types&#8221; comprised of different components. The starter themes born from it brought with them more code and styles, and gave theme authors a bigger head start in their work. The generator we built to piece the different components together got complex quickly, though. We created a plugin to test builds locally and struggled with a seamless way to make many starter themes from one code base.</p>\n<p>We learned a lot, though. We worked on Components at two team meetups, made almost 900 commits to the project and launched dozens of themes with it. However, we hit a point where we realized we had over-engineered parts of the project. The original idea is still solid: make starter themes do more by crafting them out of building blocks. But we didn&#8217;t hit the mark, so we&#8217;re retiring Components, and looking to bring some of what we learned there to Underscores.</p>\n<p>In the last year, we&#8217;ve gotten a lot of questions from the community about Underscores and whether we had abandoned it. No way! It&#8217;s a stable project, and we enjoyed working on something new, away from it. It gave us better perspective and more ideas for the future of Underscores.</p>\n<p>We also know that involvement from the community is vital. It&#8217;s been a while since we added our <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2014/04/22/commit-access-underscores/\">first contributor external to Automattic</a>. To that end, we&#8217;ve given long-time Underscores contributor <a href=\"https://github.com/grappler\">Ulrich Pogson</a> commit access. He&#8217;s also a <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/grapplerulrich/\">contributor to WordPress</a>, most frequently as a member of the Theme Review Team. We&#8217;re excited to have his expertise and passion for world-class themes as part of the project. Please join me in welcoming Ulrich! <img src=\"https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/mu-plugins/wpcom-smileys/twemoji/2/72x72/1f389.png\" alt=\"🎉\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p>It&#8217;s always hard to let go of a project, in this case, Components. But it shouldn&#8217;t be, when you walk away with more knowledge than before. It has us excited and reinvigorated about Underscores and its role in the future of theming. And we&#8217;re glad Ulrich will help us along the way!</p><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6793&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/06/26/the-future-of-underscores-and-a-new-committer/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"18\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:3:\"url\";s:63:\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2013/10/underscores.png\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"content\";a:2:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:62:\"http://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2013/10/underscores.png\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"underscores\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:82:\"http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/219860d3117df777c48f475d25e24fdd?s=96&d=identicon&r=G\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"davidalankennedy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n	\n		\n\n		\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Delightful Dara\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/04/26/dara/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/04/26/dara/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 26 Apr 2017 14:48:53 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Theme Launches\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Dara\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://themeshaper.com/?p=6787\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:677:\"Meet Dara, a beautiful new theme crafted by Caroline Moore, now available for download via WordPress.org. Dara has its roots in a popular theme called Sela. Caroline tells the story of how one theme led to another: Sela, designed and developed by the Automattic Theme Team&#8217;s Ola Bodera, remains one of our most popular themes — and &#8230; <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/04/26/dara/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> \"Delightful Dara\"</span></a><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6787&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Kathryn P.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3412:\"<p>Meet <strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/dara/\">Dara,</a></strong> a beautiful new theme crafted by <a href=\"http://carolinethemes.com/\">Caroline Moore,</a> now available for download via WordPress.org. Dara has its roots in a popular theme called Sela. Caroline tells the story of how one theme led to another:</p>\n<blockquote><p><em>Sela</em>, designed and developed by the Automattic Theme Team&#8217;s <a href=\"https://soakingupthelight.wordpress.com/\">Ola Bodera</a>, remains one of our most popular themes — and for good reason! It has a softer, sweeter quality not often seen in business themes.</p>\n<p>With <em>Dara</em>, I wanted to refine the user experience and include some of the things <em>Sela</em> users regularly asked for; moving the social links closer to the top, for example, or replacing the static image in the hero area with a slider.</p>\n<p>As someone who hangs out in the crafty space, I see <em>Sela</em> and <em>Dara</em> as perfect for small businesses and entrepreneurs who want a softer look for their sites, but the themes&#8217; flexibility and attention to detail make them lovely for personal blogs as well.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Dara supports several handy features for business users, like testmonials that let you highlight customer feedback — available through Jetpack&#8217;s Custom Content Types module.</p>\n<p>Explore the <a href=\"https://darademo.wordpress.com/\">Dara demo</a> or <a href=\"https://wordpress.com/theme/dara\">check out how to set it up</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://darademo.wordpress.com/\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6791\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/04/26/dara/ss-dara/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/ss-dara.jpg?w=840&#038;h=1820\" data-orig-size=\"1232,2669\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/ss-dara.jpg?w=840&#038;h=1820?w=138\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/ss-dara.jpg?w=840&#038;h=1820?w=473\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6791\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/ss-dara.jpg?w=840&#038;h=1820\" alt=\"Dara screenshot\" width=\"840\" height=\"1820\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/ss-dara.jpg?w=840&amp;h=1820 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/ss-dara.jpg?w=69&amp;h=150 69w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/ss-dara.jpg?w=138&amp;h=300 138w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/ss-dara.jpg?w=768&amp;h=1664 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/ss-dara.jpg?w=473&amp;h=1024 473w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/ss-dara.jpg 1232w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /></a></p><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6787&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/04/26/dara/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:2:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:82:\"http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/88ff758a54124a679af2e4cdaae8ba62?s=96&d=identicon&r=G\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"kathrynwp\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:58:\"http://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/ss-dara.jpg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Dara screenshot\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:4:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Introducing Ixion\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/03/22/introducing-ixion/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 22 Mar 2017 14:32:26 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Theme Launches\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Ixion\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://themeshaper.com/?p=6780\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:713:\"Meet Ixion, the latest theme to join our WordPress.org collection. Designed by Mel Choyce and developed by Caroline Moore, Ixion is a clean and professional theme geared to schools, non-profits, and organizations. Put your most exciting news front and center with a custom header image and a call-to-action button, highlight three noteworthy accomplishments on the &#8230; <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/03/22/introducing-ixion/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> \"Introducing Ixion\"</span></a><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6780&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Kathryn P.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2815:\"<p>Meet <strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/ixion/\">Ixion</a></strong>, the latest theme to join our WordPress.org collection. Designed by <a href=\"https://choycedesign.com/\">Mel Choyce</a> and developed by <a href=\"http://carolinethemes.com/\">Caroline Moore</a>, Ixion is a clean and professional theme geared to schools, non-profits, and organizations.</p>\n<p>Put your most exciting news front and center with a custom header image and a call-to-action button, highlight three noteworthy accomplishments on the homepage, and – with Jetpack&#8217;s Custom Content Types module &#8211; use <a href=\"https://en.support.wordpress.com/testimonials/\">Testimonials</a> to showcase your organization’s satisfied students or customers.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ixiondemo.wordpress.com/\">Visit the demo</a> or <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/ixion/\">take Ixion for a spin</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ixiondemo.wordpress.com/\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6781\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/03/22/introducing-ixion/ixion-ss/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=1403\" data-orig-size=\"1320,2205\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=1403?w=180\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=1403?w=613\" class=\"imgborder alignnone wp-image-6781 size-full\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=1403\" alt=\"Ixion screenshot\" width=\"840\" height=\"1403\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=840&amp;h=1403 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=90&amp;h=150 90w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=180&amp;h=300 180w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=768&amp;h=1283 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=613&amp;h=1024 613w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png 1320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /></a></p><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6780&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:2:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:82:\"http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/88ff758a54124a679af2e4cdaae8ba62?s=96&d=identicon&r=G\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"kathrynwp\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:59:\"http://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Ixion screenshot\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n	\n		\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"Content Options in Jetpack 4.5\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 27 Jan 2017 15:32:25 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Theme Development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Content Options\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"customizer\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Jetpack\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://themeshaper.com/?p=6754\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:329:\"Now available through Jetpack, Content Options let users make small visual changes, like showing or hiding the author, date, featured images, and more.<img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6754&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Thomas Guillot\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17687:\"<p><a href=\"https://en.blog.wordpress.com/2016/08/30/introducing-content-options-an-easy-new-way-to-make-visual-changes-to-your-site/\">Last August</a>, we introduced a new WordPress.com Customizer panel called Content Options, which gives users an easy way to make small visual modifications across their sites – no custom CSS needed.</p>\n<p>Content Options supports four main features: <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5#blog-display\">Blog Display</a>, <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5#author-bio\">Author Bio</a>, <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5#post-details\">Post Details</a>, and <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5#featured-images\">Featured Images</a>.</p>\n<p>Content Options are now available to self-hosted WordPress sites with the latest version of <a href=\"https://jetpack.com/\">Jetpack</a> (4.5). Theme developers can add support for Content Options by following the <a href=\"https://jetpack.com/support/content-options/\">Jetpack guide</a>.</p>\n<p>Let&#8217;s look at the main features of Content Options in more detail.</p>\n<h2 id=\"blog-display\">Blog Display</h2>\n<p>Users can choose between displaying the full content of each post or an <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Excerpt\">excerpt</a> on the blog and category, tag, and date archive pages, as well as search results.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_6760\" style=\"width: 840px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6760\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/content-options-blog-display-full/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=840&#038;h=704\" data-orig-size=\"945,792\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=840&#038;h=704?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=840&#038;h=704?w=840\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6760\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=840&#038;h=704\" alt=\"Full post blog display option in Shoreditch\" width=\"840\" height=\"704\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=840&amp;h=704 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=150&amp;h=126 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=300&amp;h=251 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=768&amp;h=644 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Full post blog display option in Shoreditch</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_6761\" style=\"width: 840px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6761\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/content-options-blog-display-excerpt/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=840&#038;h=294\" data-orig-size=\"953,334\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=840&#038;h=294?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=840&#038;h=294?w=840\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6761\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=840&#038;h=294\" alt=\"Post excerpt blog display option in Shoreditch\" width=\"840\" height=\"294\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=840&amp;h=294 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=150&amp;h=53 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=300&amp;h=105 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=768&amp;h=269 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png 953w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Post excerpt blog display option in Shoreditch</figcaption></figure>\n<p><strong>Default Blog Display</strong></p>\n<p>If a theme displays either an excerpt or the full post depending on the post’s post format, theme developers can add a &#8220;Default&#8221; blog display option to let the theme keep its default blog display settings. For example, by default a theme might always displays posts with the Quote post format as the full post, so a quote is never truncated, while other post formats like Standard might be always displayed as an excerpt.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_6762\" style=\"width: 840px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6762\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/content-options-blog-display-default/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=840&#038;h=823\" data-orig-size=\"1204,1179\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=840&#038;h=823?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=840&#038;h=823?w=840\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6762\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=840&#038;h=823\" alt=\"Default blog display option in Button\" width=\"840\" height=\"823\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=840&amp;h=823 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=150&amp;h=147 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=300&amp;h=294 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=768&amp;h=752 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=1024&amp;h=1003 1024w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png 1204w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Default blog display option in Button</figcaption></figure>\n<h2 id=\"author-bio\">Author Bio</h2>\n<p>On the single post view, users can opt to display the name and bio of the post&#8217;s author. This information comes directly from the author’s profile at Users <span class=\"st\">→</span> Your Profile, and their <a href=\"https://gravatar.com/\">Gravatar</a> image.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_6755\" style=\"width: 840px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6755\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/content-options-author-bio/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-author-bio.png?w=840&#038;h=427\" data-orig-size=\"952,484\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-author-bio.png?w=840&#038;h=427?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-author-bio.png?w=840&#038;h=427?w=840\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6755\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-author-bio.png?w=840&#038;h=427\" alt=\"Author Bio displayed on single post in Shoreditch\" width=\"840\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-author-bio.png?w=840&amp;h=427 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-author-bio.png?w=150&amp;h=76 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-author-bio.png?w=300&amp;h=153 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-author-bio.png?w=768&amp;h=390 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-author-bio.png 952w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Author bio displayed on single post in Shoreditch</figcaption></figure>\n<h2 id=\"post-details\">Post Details</h2>\n<p>The post details section allows users to show or hide the post date, categories, tags, or the post author’s name.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_6756\" style=\"width: 840px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6756\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/content-options-post-details/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details.png?w=840&#038;h=724\" data-orig-size=\"964,831\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details.png?w=840&#038;h=724?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details.png?w=840&#038;h=724?w=840\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6756\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details.png?w=840&#038;h=724\" alt=\"Post Details displayed in Penscratch\" width=\"840\" height=\"724\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details.png?w=840&amp;h=724 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details.png?w=150&amp;h=129 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details.png?w=300&amp;h=259 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details.png?w=768&amp;h=662 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details.png 964w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Post details displayed in Penscratch</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_6757\" style=\"width: 840px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6757\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/content-options-post-details-hidden/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details-hidden.png?w=840&#038;h=641\" data-orig-size=\"964,736\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details-hidden.png?w=840&#038;h=641?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details-hidden.png?w=840&#038;h=641?w=840\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6757\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details-hidden.png?w=840&#038;h=641\" alt=\"Post Details hidden in Penscratch\" width=\"840\" height=\"641\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details-hidden.png?w=840&amp;h=641 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details-hidden.png?w=150&amp;h=115 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details-hidden.png?w=300&amp;h=229 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details-hidden.png?w=768&amp;h=586 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-post-details-hidden.png 964w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Post details hidden in Penscratch</figcaption></figure>\n<h2 id=\"featured-images\">Featured Images</h2>\n<p>Users can choose whether to display featured images on single posts and pages. They can also opt whether to display featured images on blog and archive pages, which include category, tag, and date archives as well as search-results pages.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_6758\" style=\"width: 840px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6758\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/content-options-featured-images/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-featured-images.png?w=840&#038;h=420\" data-orig-size=\"1191,595\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-featured-images.png?w=840&#038;h=420?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-featured-images.png?w=840&#038;h=420?w=840\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6758\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-featured-images.png?w=840&#038;h=420\" alt=\"Featured Images displayed in Sela\" width=\"840\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-featured-images.png?w=840&amp;h=420 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-featured-images.png?w=150&amp;h=75 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-featured-images.png?w=300&amp;h=150 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-featured-images.png?w=768&amp;h=384 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-featured-images.png?w=1024&amp;h=512 1024w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-featured-images.png 1191w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Featured images displayed in Sela</figcaption></figure>\n<p>WordPress.com users have loved the flexibility Content Options gives them. We&#8217;re very pleased that self-hosted sites can now benefit as well!</p><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6754&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5